window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A city on the brink. A hero on the rise.</b></p> <p>Things have been quiet ever since we took down the makers of the Green Machine drug, but it’s only the calm before the storm. When Sorvak unleashes the final part of his savage plan for retribution, it forces the battered city to its knees.</p> <p>Many think we’re better off surrendering. Quite a few want to abandon Thornveil City altogether, but I refuse to admit defeat. With my women standing beside me, we’ll risk everything just to save our home.</p> <p>My enemies will soon learn that a lion bows to no one.</p> <p><b>Join me for the ultimate conclusion to Shifter City Hero!</b></p>"; 
